---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-rule mt-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[64rem] px-6 py-14">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-5">colophon</p>
    <blockquote
      class="font-serif italic text-ink-dim leading-relaxed text-[0.97rem] max-w-3xl"
      style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 16, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 0;"
    >
      &ldquo;<span class="font-semibold not-italic text-ink">Pure intent</span>
      is a palpable life-force; an actually occurring stream of benevolence and
      benignity that originates in the vast and utter stillness that is the
      essential character of the universe itself&hellip;
      With pure intent running as a
      <span class="text-amber not-italic">golden thread</span>
      through one&rsquo;s life, reflective contemplation about being here doing
      this business called being alive rapidly becomes more and more
      fascinating.&rdquo;
    </blockquote>
    <p class="mt-3 mono text-[0.7rem] text-ink-muted tracking-widest">
      —&nbsp;Richard,
      <a
        href="https://actualfreedom.com.au/richard/abditorium/pureintent.htm"
        rel="noopener"
        class="hover:text-amber transition-colors"
      >
        on pure intent ↗
      </a>
    </p>

    <hr class="border-rule my-10" />

    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-4 mono text-[0.72rem] text-ink-muted"
    >
      <div class="space-y-1">
        <div>© {year} Sridhar Ratnakumar · MIT</div>
        <div>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/srid/agency"
            rel="noopener"
            class="hover:text-amber transition-colors"
          >
            github.com/srid/agency ↗
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:text-right text-ink-faint">
        Sister project ·
        <a
          href="https://kolu.dev"
          rel="noopener"
          class="hover:text-amber transition-colors">kolu.dev ↗</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
